{"tid":1616931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係話敵人反對我哋就要支持咩？","createTime":"2019-10-03T14:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T03:44:48.000Z","uid":62369,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"54f330afbf319f6020f3740bf4a23fc55c8edcdc","tid":1616931,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:53:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">敵人要立反蒙面法，即係代表佢好驚我哋蒙晒面！<br />\n因為佢哋認我哋唔到捉我哋唔到，所以先要出此下策！<br />\n既然敵人最驚我哋蒙面，咁我哋更加要蒙面蒙到阿媽都唔認得！<br />\n<br />\n我唔想再見到啲手足戴口罩戴到甩晒，我仲見到你個樣呀！<br />\n有啲仲連口罩都唔戴！<br />\n唔該飲水唔好扯低個口罩嚟飲，全程都唔好露樣，如果唔係前功盡廢。<br />\n我想見到大家由頭遮到落腳，唔好再俾我見到你啲眼耳口鼻！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ce7cf88b2015d5023cf0a2502b467213429f9d81","tid":1616931,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:54:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8526634c396e600ee57081932a0c6e7719d24448","tid":1616931,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:54:49.000Z","msg":"咪再比我見到樣呀！"},{"pid":"1f996c8162d05fe34fc0dc270245bfc0ab1d3124","tid":1616931,"uid":266279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ad96812f53161070e8213d1e13fed65139ed1d","tid":1616931,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:55:09.000Z","msg":"咪再曝露自己行蹤呀！"},{"pid":"682e7700682add6b425d75b2f25502bdb36a520a","tid":1616931,"uid":62369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:55:35.000Z","msg":"咪再係街討論發夢嘅嘢呀！"},{"pid":"1eb6f84d511167b428e9f35c40a